{"tid":697099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［又冇人報］越南爆發咗反中國示威 抗議俾中國租用'經濟特區'","createTime":"2018-06-10T16:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-11T00:32:40.000Z","uid":48083,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"988be34c7ceeedfad2fd0683abd713a94666c82d","tid":697099,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"Protests have broken out in Vietnam against plans for three new economic zones, amid fears that Chinese investors will dominate the areas.<br />\n<br />\nPolice reportedly detained more than a dozen people in the capital Hanoi and halted demonstrations in other cities.<br />\n<br />\nSome carried anti-China banners, including one reading: &quot;No leasing land to China even for one day.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe government proposed a law last year that would give foreign investors a 99-year lease on Vietnamese land.<br />\n<br />\nThe bill offers them greater incentives and fewer restrictions, in an attempt to promote growth in target areas.<br />\n<br />\nThe protesters suspect that the communist government will award Chinese investors leases in the three economic zones in the north-east, south-east and south-west of the country, and that this would be a pretext for Chinese control over the island of Van Don near their shared border.<br />\n<br />\nVietnam won a naval battle against a Mongolian fleet off the island in 1287, and some Vietnamese people fear their government will give it away amid tensions between the two countries over disputed territory in the South China Sea.<br />\n<br />\nWhy is the South China Sea contentious?<br />\nUS: China is 'intimidating neighbours'<br />\nPrime Minister Nguyen Xuan Phuc last week told local media the 99-year term would be reduced, although he did not specify the new length.<br />\n<br />\nAnd on Saturday, the government announced a vote on the draft legislation would be delayed to allow further scrutiny.<br />\n<br />\nDemonstrators are also objecting to a cyber security bill, scheduled for a vote on 12 June. Human Rights Watch say it would give the government broad powers quash dissent online.<br />\n<br />\nRoughly $5 trillion worth of global trade passes through the South China Sea annually, and a number of countries claim disputed islands in the area.<br />\n<br />\nVietnamese protests broke out in 2012 over the maritime dispute, although police quickly halted the demonstrations.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-44428971\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-44428971&d=9ZkRbwUhydai648jsR7k%2BJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=efbb6663\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-44428971</a><br />\n<br />\n得scmp有講吓"},{"pid":"106e5b28fc1c46097ccd103974544d074c7ba759","tid":697099,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00bf57ab86d60307860be0a17ca6b21043606f6d","tid":697099,"uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"贏国一於趁全世界去左新加坡，乘機出兵佔領經濟特區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb98c7c8f59f0db6826266a04a707626b8e87238","tid":697099,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc313593c6db13d2b4bf905f12d1ddf11cf6eee1","tid":697099,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:24:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"283d2dd7c5751f23e0c488d8c83109f8bf0972ed","tid":697099,"uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:30:26.000Z","msg":"反經濟特區租地給中國等外商99年 越南各大城爆抗議<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/003025_24a0a91e887f8136b30e3642b5602ab2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F003025_24a0a91e887f8136b30e3642b5602ab2.png&h=85792682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕越南政府擬定於15日通過的「經濟特區法草案」，預計規劃3個經濟特區，供外商租借，最高可達99年。引起民眾相當不滿，越南人今（10）聚集在各大城市，手拿標語布條遊行抗議，與警方爆發衝突，有媒體目擊民眾遭便衣警察強拉上鄰近巴士。在首都河內（Hanoi）至少有12人遭到逮捕。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n綜合外電報導，這份「經濟特區法」草案，擬定在北部沿岸的廣寧省雲屯縣（Van Don）、中部慶和省北雲峰縣（Bac Van Phong）及南部堅江省富國島（Phu Quoc）設立3個經濟特區，計畫給予外商租地期限最長延至99年等優惠。這讓民眾認為是圖利外商，尤其是中國企業，引發民眾不滿，質疑這將對國家領土主權、政治、移民管理等問題產生不利影響。<br />\n<br />\n民眾透過網路號召群眾上街，當地今天上午在各大城市如河內、義安（Nghe An）、芽莊（Nha Trang）與胡志明市等地集結，手拿「反對經濟特區法草案」、「即便只有一天也不租給中國！」等標語遊行抗議，卻遭到警方驅離，爆發肢體衝突。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》特派員目睹，在河內約有20名抗議人士遭便衣警察拖離並架上鄰近巴士。民眾也透過社群軟體發布現場情形，甚至有抗議人士遭到警方毆打，傷勢嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n越南國會本來預計在15日批准通過這項草案。由於民眾激烈反對，越南國會法律委員會表示，會將外商租地期限最長可達99年的優惠，縮減至50年，特殊情況可申請延期，但最長不超過70年。草案也將延後至年底會議再通過，期間會進一步徵求各界意見。<br />\n<br />\n越南政府預料人民將在今天舉行抗議活動，提前在位於胡志明市的中國領事館架好層層拒馬，並且派駐多名警力駐守，不過抗議人士蔓延在各大城市與街道上，甚至在日本也有越南人民集結表示「越南土地必須由越南人決定」。<br />\n<br />\n相關連結<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2453880\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2453880&d=9ZkRbwUhydai648jsR7k%2BJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=066568be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2453880&h=c9bc024f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2453880</a>"},{"pid":"390d8ed746601390de41271b208b1a192d0acde6","tid":697099,"uid":8410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:31:28.000Z","msg":"排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n越南好多支那遊客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d557a32afb87c904f15c6d27c183848b1ef9595a","tid":697099,"uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:32:22.000Z","msg":"同場加映撚屌賤種打手mk輝既平行時空鳩噏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯國自2004年起，已經是越南最大貿易顆伴，雙方邊境城市也有「兩廊一圈」經濟區，再要進一步融合，越南就有被「消化」的憂慮<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">。其中越南北部對中國的投資較歡迎，</span></span>南部則持觀望態度⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ir-basilica.com/【沈旭暉專欄】「一帶一路」時代，屬貓的越南人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ir-basilica.com%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B2%88%E6%97%AD%E6%9A%89%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84%E3%80%91%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF%E3%80%8D%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%EF%BC%8C%E5%B1%AC%E8%B2%93%E7%9A%84%E8%B6%8A%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%BA%2F&d=9ZkRbwUhydai648jsR7k%2BJUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=25f9ff2a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ir-basilica.com/【沈旭暉專欄】「一帶一路」時代，屬貓的越南人/</a>"},{"pid":"a0bb066900b3f8e7b4648ad172b57433dc9c2dc8","tid":697099,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f69a7ba1c5701f101db82875e902521f19ac826b","tid":697099,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"a0bb066900b3f8e7b4648ad172b57433dc9c2dc8","tid":697099,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:33:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:34:27.000Z","msg":"咁中國呢？"},{"pid":"63ab94a1b130bda331eb84261c8f75de66010da9","tid":697099,"uid":20227,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e53b4064ac73b61486448641f8549ec51dd0db9","tid":697099,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:34:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53fd66a14dce549dd7834ac981d4d60512f0ccac","tid":697099,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:35:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6fb8e9fe389f76ddcad5bf029029e7324338ecb1","tid":697099,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0